 Dynamic Video Resources (YouTube API).\nTech Stack: Python 3.x, Flask, Flask-SQLAlchemy, Flask-Migrate, Google Gemini, YouTube Data API v3, Flask-Login, Flask-HTTPAuth, pythondotenv.\n\n[README Content for git-agent]\nAutomating social media content generation from GitHub commit logs using AI.\nFeatures: Automated Commit Analysis, AIPowered Content Generation (Gemini via Langchain), MultiPlatform Posting, Asynchronous Processing (RQ/Redis), Stateful Workflows (LangGraph with PostgresSaver), RESTful API.\nTech Stack: Python 3.x, Flask, Google Gemini, LangGraph, Langchain, PostgreSQL, Flask-SQLAlchemy, RQ (Redis Queue), Redis, Flask-HTTPAuth, Pandas, Pydantic.\n\n[README Content for hospital_agents / hospital_agent]\nModular Flask applications for reactive AI agent orchestration.\nFeatures: Asynchronous Request Handling (Redis Streams), LangGraph State Machine, Modular Flask (Blueprint/Factory pattern), API Development, Event-driven architecture.\nTech Stack: Python 3.x, Flask, LangGraph, Redis, SQLAlchemy, threading, langchain_core.'}
