w.\n\nmedai:\n- Tools & Tech Stack: Python 3.x, Flask, Flask-SQLAlchemy, Flask-Migrate, Google Gemini, YouTube Data API v3, Flask-Login, Flask-HTTPAuth, Werkzeug, python-dotenv.\n- Features: Conversational AI assistant, RESTful API endpoints, User management (anonymous/registered), Structured medical info extraction.\n\ngit-agent:\n- Tools & Tech Stack: Python 3.x, Flask, Google Gemini, LangGraph, LangChain, PostgreSQL, SQLAlchemy, RQ (Redis Queue), Flask-Login, Flask-HTTPAuth, Pandas, Pydantic.\n- Features: Automated commit analysis, AI-powered content generation, Multi-platform posting, Asynchronous processing, RESTful API.\n\nhospital_agents / hospital_agent:\n- Tools & Tech Stack: Python 3.x, Flask, LangGraph, Redis (Streams), SQLAlchemy, langchain_core, threading, pytest.\n- Features: Asynchronous request processing, State machine management, Reactive event-driven architecture.', 'job_description': 'We are looking for a Machine Learning Engineer with experience in Python, FastAPI, Docker, LLMs, and building scalable AI systems.', 'base_summary': 'Experienced Machine Learning Engineer with a proven track record in building scalable AI systems and conversational agents. Highly proficient in designing agentic workflows using LangGraph and LangChain, integrating LLMs (Google Gemini) for structured information extraction, and developing robust RESTful APIs in Python. Expertise in building asynchronous, event-driven architectures with Redis to handle complex, scalable AI workloads.'}
