my', 'Flask-Login', 'Flask-HTTPAuth', 'anyio', 'asyncio', 'RQ', 'YouTube API', 'Geoapify API'], 'projects': [{'name': 'Medic AI Agent', 'bullets': ['Architected a stateful agentic workflow using LangGraph to orchestrate complex medical triage logic.', 'Implemented Pydantic schemas to enforce structured data extraction from unstructured natural language inputs.', 'Integrated external YouTube and Geoapify APIs to provide context-aware, real-time first-aid guidance.', 'Built scalable AI systems capable of handling asynchronous user interactions via Redis message queuing.']}, {'name': 'Git-Agent', 'bullets': ['Designed a stateful workflow for automating social media content generation from GitHub commit logs.', 'Deployed PostgreSQL for persistent checkpointing, ensuring fault-tolerant execution of long-running AI tasks.', 'Utilized RQ and Redis to decouple heavy LLM processing from the main application thread, improving system scalability.']}, {'bullets': ['Engineered an asynchronous AI orchestration layer using Flask and LangGraph to manage hospital-related tasks.', 'Leveraged Redis Streams to facilitate efficient, non-blocking communication between agentic components.', 'Optimized background task processing to support high-concurrency environments in a production-ready architecture.'], 'name': 'Hospital Agents'}, {'name': 'Medai', 'bullets': ['Developed a conversational AI assistant featuring RESTful API design for managing user sessions and chat history.', 'Integrated Flask-SQLAlchemy to manage secure user authentication and persistent medical information storage.', 'Implemented structured medical information extraction pipelines powered by Google Gemini LLM integration.']}], 'skills': ['Machine Learning Engineering', 'LLM Orchestration', 'Scalable AI Systems', 'Autonomous Workflow Design', 'Prompt Engineering', 'API Design', 'Asynchronous Task Processing', 'Data Validation', 'Stateful Workflow Management', 'Conversational AI Development', 'Structured Data Extraction